Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
metric_capture...exclude_layers(25.10)  metric_capture...exclude_layers(25.10)

Name
       metric_capture_design_image_blockages_exclude_layers

Syntax
        metric_capture_design_image_blockages_exclude_layers <layer_names>

       Default: ""

       Specifies a list of layers to exclude when capturing the blockage image
       metric (design.blockage.image). For example, it can be useful for skip-
       ping blockages related to metal fill.

